summary:
Borut Kirn applies 20+ years of experiences in Human Physiology, Medical measurements and Complex data analyzing into medical device development and evaluation. His basic education is in Physics. 
As an entrepreneur, he is applying Lean Start-Up concepts in decentralized platform development for internet based medical solutions. Living between Maastricht (NL) and Ljubljana (SI), he is well traveled and fluent in several European languages.
